         <h3 class="block-header">
          Alumni
          <span>
           Events
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p style="text-align: center;">
           <img alt="" height="252" src="images/images/alumni-weekend-band.jpg" width="379"/>
          </p>
          <div style="text-align: left;">
           We are always excited to host Banana Slug alumni events regionally and locally! Whether you want to find resources, network with other alumni, or just have fun - your UC Santa Cruz Alumni community has something for you.
           <a href="events/calendar.html">
            Click here
           </a>
           for a full calendar of our upcoming events.
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
